===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# {{math}} {{uncountable}} A system for computation using letters or other symbols to represent numbers, with rules for manipulating these symbols.
# {{algebra}} A structure consisting of a set of [[element]]s together with one or more [[operations]] and rules specifying what expressions are equivalent.
# {{algebra}} {{uncountable}} The study of algebras.

